coding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>스텝 4 : 스택의 최상단 노드인 ‘7’에 방문하지 않은 인접 노드인 ‘6’, ’8’ 중 작은 쪽인 6을 스택에 넣고 방문 처리합니다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.888888888888886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-04-27 at 8.50.17 PM.png\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2022-04-27 at 8.50.17 PM.png\"\n        src=\"/static/431776788e2534ca0311081f4acd026f/37523/018_04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/431776788e2534ca0311081f4acd026f/e9ff0/018_04.png 180w,\n/static/431776788e2534ca0311081f4acd026f/f21e7/018_04.png 360w,\n/static/431776788e2534ca0311081f4acd026f/37523/018_04.png 720w,\n/static/431776788e2534ca0311081f4acd026f/302a4/018_04.png 1080w,\n/static/431776788e2534ca0311081f4acd026f/bb543/018_04.png 1418w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>스텝 5 : 그런데 스텍 최상단 노드인 ‘6’ 에 방문하지 않은 인접 노드가 없다면, 6 노드를 꺼냅니다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-04-27 at 8.49.09 PM.png\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2022-04-27 at 8.49.09 PM.png\"\n        src=\"/static/30efb8c273b7de119009b640b6f37f1e/37523/018_05.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/30efb8c273b7de119009b640b6f37f1e/e9ff0/018_05.png 180w,\n/static/30efb8c273b7de119009b640b6f37f1e/f21e7/018_05.png 360w,\n/static/30efb8c273b7de119009b640b6f37f1e/37523/018_05.png 720w,\n/static/30efb8c273b7de119009b640b6f37f1e/302a4/018_05.png 1080w,\n/static/30efb8c273b7de119009b640b6f37f1e/07a9c/018_05.png 1440w,\n/static/30efb8c273b7de119009b640b6f37f1e/bd9eb/018_05.png 1442w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>스텝 6 : 스택의 최 상단 노드인 ‘7’에 방문하지 않은 인접 노드 8이 있으므로 스택에 넣고 방문 처리를 합니다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.222222222222214%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-04-27 at 8.51.27 PM.png\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2022-04-27 at 8.51.27 PM.png\"\n        src=\"/static/eabae351deaecddb1c59428740126e9c/37523/018_06.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eabae351deaecddb1c59428740126e9c/e9ff0/018_06.png 180w,\n/static/eabae351deaecddb1c59428740126e9c/f21e7/018_06.png 360w,\n/static/eabae351deaecddb1c59428740126e9c/37523/018_06.png 720w,\n/static/eabae351deaecddb1c59428740126e9c/302a4/018_06.png 1080w,\n/static/eabae351deaecddb1c59428740126e9c/daed9/018_06.png 1426w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n